{"componentsInOrder": [{"type": "TEXT_BOX", "details": {"textList": [{"text": "Rummy is a game of skill where the cards are dealt randomly. We always want to provide a fair platform to our customers, and hence we use a Random Number Generator (RNG) to distribute all cards.
