{"componentsInOrder": [{"type": "TEXT_BOX", "details": {"textList": [{"text": "Exit action is available when your opinion has been matched with another user and is in matched status. As the price of “Yes” or “No” keeps fluctuating, you can exit your order at any time before the question ends to book your profits or minimise your loss (even before the question results are out.) 

